  "vulnerability_information": "It's possible to take over subdomains that point to GitLab Pages. While adding a subdomain no verification of domain ownership is required.\n\n## POC Steps \n\n1. Go to http://george.ratelimited.me/ (tested in Firefox)\n\n\n{F3307364}\n\n## Impact\n\nAttackers could perform several attacks like:\n\n  -  Cookie Stealing\n  - Phishing campaigns.\n  -  Bypass Content-Security Policies and CORS.",
